# Privacy Policy for Tonepitch

Last updated: April 1, 2025

## Introduction

Tonepitch ("we," "our," or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application (the "App").

## Information We Collect

### Information You Provide
- We do not collect any personal information directly from you
- The App does not require any user accounts or registration

### Information Automatically Collected
- **Audio Processing**: The app uses your device's microphone only for real-time pitch analysis
  - All audio processing happens entirely on your device
  - We do not store or transmit any audio data
- **AdMob Data**: Our advertising partner (Google AdMob) may collect:
  - Device identifiers (Advertising ID)
  - IP address
  - Cookie data
  - Usage data and interaction with ads
  - General location data (based on IP address)

## Third-Party Services

### Google AdMob
The app uses Google AdMob for advertisements. AdMob's data collection practices are governed by Google's Privacy Policy: [https://policies.google.com/privacy](https://policies.google.com/privacy)

### Advertising Data Usage
To serve personalized ads (where permitted by law), our ad partners may:
- Collect device information (model, OS version)
- Use interest-based advertising
- Share data with third-party advertisers

To opt out of personalized ads:
1. Open your device Settings
2. Go to Privacy â†’ Ads
3. Enable "Opt out of Ads Personalization"

## Data Security
- All audio processing is done locally on your device
- We implement industry-standard security measures
- Third-party services (AdMob) follow their own security protocols

## Children's Privacy
- The App is suitable for all ages
- For users under 13:
  - We disable personalized ads
  - Only contextual ads are shown
  - We comply with the Children's Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA)
- Parents can contact us about their children's data

## Your Rights
You have the right to:
- Access your data
- Request deletion of stored data
- Opt out of personalized advertising
- Contact us about privacy concerns

## Changes to This Privacy Policy
- We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time
- We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page
- Continued use after changes implies acceptance

## Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
tonepitch1@gmail.com

## California Privacy Rights
- We do not sell your personal information
- AdMob may collect data for advertising purposes
- You can opt out of personalized advertising as described above

## European Union Privacy Rights
- We comply with GDPR requirements
- Data collection is limited to what is necessary for app functionality and advertising
- You can exercise your data rights as described in "Your Rights" section 
